<doc id="366216" wikidata="Q56068830" url="?curid=366216" title="Spice Girl (disambiguation)">
<text>A Spice Girl is a member of English girl group the Spice Girls.

Spice Girl may also refer to:

* &quot;Spice Girl&quot;, a song by rapper Aminé on the album &quot;Good for You&quot;
