*Swainson, W. 1843. Flycatchers. Ornithology. Volume XIII, Jardine&#x27;s Naturalist&#x27;s Library [xvi], t.e.g. Edinburgh: W. H. Lizars.
*Swainson W. Ornithology Birds of Western Africa- Part 1 1862. The Naturalists Library, W Jardine (ed) Vol XI. (A reprint of 1837)
==See also==
*:Category:Taxa named by William Swainson

